ards|UEFA Euro 2008 Team of the Tournament]]<ref name=\"en.euro2008.uefa.com\" />\n*[[UEFA Euro 2008|UEFA Euro 2008 Man of the Match]]: Spain vs [[Russia national football team|Russia]], Spain vs [[Sweden national football team|Sweden]]\n*[[2009 FIFA Confederations Cup#Awards|2009 FIFA Confederations Cup Bronze Shoe]]\n*[[2009 FIFA Confederations Cup#Awards|2009 FIFA Confederations Cup Team of the Tournament]].<ref name=\"confed 11\" />\n*[[Don Bal\u00f3n Award|Spanish Player of the Year]]: [[2005\u201306 La Liga|2005\u201306]]\n*[[Zarra Trophy]]: [[2005\u201306 La Liga|2005\u201306]], [[2006\u201307 La Liga|2006\u201307]], [[2008\u201309 La Liga|2008\u201309]], [[2009\u201310 La Liga|2009\u201310]]\n*[[United States Sports Academy|USSA Male Athlete of the Year]]: 2010\n*[[Landon Donovan MVP Award|MLS MVP]]: 2016<ref name=\"MVP\"/>\n*[[MLS Best XI]]: [[2016 Major League Soccer season#MLS Best XI|2016]],<ref>{{cite web |title=MLS Best XI revealed: Who was the best at each position in 2016? |url=http://www.mlssoccer.com/post/2016/12/05/mls-best-xi-revealed-who-was-best-each-position-2016 |date=5 December 2016 |access-date=6 December 2016 |work=[[MLS Soccer]]}}</ref> [[2017 Major League Soccer season#MLS Best XI|2017]]<ref name=\"2017 MLS Best XI\">{{cite web |url=https://www.mlssoccer.com/post/2017/11/29/2017-mls-best-xi |title=2017 MLS Best XI revealed: Who was the best in 2017? |work=[[MLS Soccer]] |date=30 November 2017 |access-date=4 December 2017}}</ref>\n*[[Major League Soccer All-Star Game|MLS All-Star]]: [[2015 MLS All-Star Game|2015]],<ref name=\"AT&T MLS All-Star Game roster\">{{cite web|url=http://www.mlssoccer.com/all-star/2015/news/article/2015/07/18/sebastian-giovinco-kei-kamara-among-22-players-named-2015-att-mls-all-star-g|title=Sebastian Giovinco, Kei Kamara among 22 players named to 2015 AT&T MLS All-Star Game roster|date=20 July 2015|publisher=Major League Soccer|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150921022035/http://www.mlssoccer.com/all-star